data.description:
Welcome to your forever home! This gem boasts a 3-car garage and an A.O. Smith Water Filtration System for pure drinking water. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, with a large kitchen island and stainless steel appliances. Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the chilly months. The big laundry room with storage keeps things organized. Don't forget the RV parking and custom gates for added convenience. No more HOA headaches - make this dream home yours today! The plantation shutters and custom shades add an elegant touch to every room, creating a sense of privacy and tranquility. Furthermore, the A.O. Smith Water filtration system ensures that you and your loved ones always have access to clean and pure water throughout the house.

Outside, you'll find a remarkable landscape featuring a garden and a beautifully landscaped front and backyard, all enclosed by 9 ft brick walls for added security and privacy. The custom gates add a touch of sophistication and ensure the safety of your vehicles and RV in the dedicated parking area.

Situated in the coveted Little valley Community, this home comes with numerous perks. Enjoy access to fantastic schools, impeccable pickleball courts, and sprawling parks just moments away. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your forever home!
